; programma azzeramento macchina
; Move to the machine origin.         
G53 G0 X0 Y0 Z0 A0 
; Clear the G92 coordinate offset.    
G92.1
; Use the G54 coordinate system.      
G54
; Set the G54 coordinate system to be identical to the machine  coordinate system. 
G10 L2 P1 X0 Y0 Z0 A0 
; Turn off tool offsets.              
G49
M2
